			</div><!--/col-lg-4 -->

			<div class="col-lg-4">
				<%= image_tag('ser03.png', :width => "180") %>
				<h4>Accurate Voice Recognition Algorithm</h4>
				<p>No longer will you need to bury your nose while delivering a presentation or speech. Just speak with your heart, and AutoFlip will follow along. When you get stuck, just glance down and your most relevant talking point will be waiting for you.</p>

			</div><!--/col-lg-4 -->
		</div><!-- /row -->
	</div><!-- /container -->
	
